<ContentLayout
  title="SEO Audit for Healthcare Websites: YMYL, E-E-A-T, and Medical SEO"
  description="Healthcare websites face the highest SEO scrutiny from Google. Learn how to audit medical content for E-E-A-T compliance, YMYL standards, and HIPAA considerations."
